ean into to stay grounded, nourished and", "energized?", "6. How have you learned to keep yourself in flow? How do you navigate some of your", "challenges such as over-giving, trying to do everything yourself and fear of trusting", "others?", "7. What is your advice for other Divine Feminine leaders in general? What is", "your advice to Divine Feminine leaders looking to create their own generative", "communities including possible archetypal pitfalls?", "Copyright 2020. Priscilla Stephan. All Rights Reserved. www.priscillastephan.com", "Content licensed exclusively to Soulfluent LLC.", "www.priscillastephan.com"], "bbox": [[0.223998, 0.100576, 0.54561, 0.102735], [0.439418, 0.186605, 0.12123000000000006, 0.031314], [0.294194, 0.290764, -0.007116000000000011, 0.019451], [0.150196, 0.323773, -0.007116000000000011, 0.019451], [0.084559, 0.345866, 0.793871, 0.019385], [0.084559, 0.367959, 0.326147, 0.019385], [0.218531, 0.400968, -0.006330000000000002, 0.019451], [0.084559, 0.423062, 0.45640200000000003, 0.019385], [0.084559, 0.488702, 0.48172200000000004, 0.019451], [0.099258, 0.516212, 0.7858630000000001, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.538305, 0.138688, 0.019385], [0.099258, 0.566078, 0.7721410000000001, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.588171, 0.093719, 0.019385], [0.099258, 0.615944, 0.804769, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.638038, 0.359858, 0.019385], [0.099258, 0.66581, 0.798544, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.687904, 0.05988099999999999, 0.019385], [0.099258, 0.715677, 0.721099, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.73777, 0.10225799999999999, 0.019385], [0.099258, 0.765543, 0.8016880000000001, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.787636, 0.765429, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.80973, 0.07011900000000001, 0.019385], [0.099258, 0.837502, 0.7061000000000001, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.859596, 0.7130460000000001, 0.019385], [0.128678, 0.881689, 0.4696990000000001, 0.019385], [0.176271, 0.927146, 0.647467, 0.014722], [0.313362, 0.942298, 0.3732520000000001, 0.014722], [0.37607, 0.97166, 0.24786300000000006, 0.017667]], "score": [1